<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>CRUD App</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Welcome to the CRUD App</h1>
  <p>Use the following routes to perform CRUD operations:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>GET /crud - View all items</li>
    <li>POST /crud/add - Add a new item</li>
    <li>GET /crud/:id - View a single item</li>
    <li>PUT /crud/update/:id - Update an item</li>
    <li>DELETE /crud/delete/:id - Delete an item</li>
  </ul>
</body>
</html>
